column5: Any one going to be in the Hudson area of Lac Suel June 5th thru 11th? I will be at Deer Path Lodge
Will be in that area June26 - July 2. You have any hot spots, or GPS digits?
I will be fishing the NE section( Taylor Island > Wapesi Bay ) July 2-9. How can I help? J.B. Patton
Who are you staying with. We were up for the opener and started at Lac Seul Floating Lodges and went up to Tucky. We fished that area and up into Chamberlin. Bob
